The paper deals with data compression and transmission policies for energy-constrained sensor nodes, which is a common problem in wireless sensor networks. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of compression algorithms, which could place it in the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses optimization problems, which could suggest it belongs to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
